column5: I am all in. This will be my third Movember.  Started today and already have a nice one carved in.  Not a huge cookie duster like the last couple of years.  This year I am going with a frech styled three musketeers look. My wife hates this month. lol.
Ya I started a beard in october so I can get a decent start on my shideous stache....just cuz the girlfriend bet me I wouldn't.
i haven't shaved in almost a month.  i'm already working on my decembeard.
Another 6 weeks (if I make it that far) and I should almost look like Santa, again.  Question....  What's a razor?
IN,  We have an office team going. There will be some "lames" for sure lol. . MoStyleGuide.pdf
I'm in but I have shaved my lip and chin in 8 or more years so does it count?
I'm in and have the cheesiest dirtstick you'll ever see. Gets plenty of laughs, so I'll keep it around.
i got mine going about 2 weeks ago! damn it gets itchy!!
I'm in...got an interesting thing going on...actually I feel like the Leafs because I can't help but laugh when I look in the mirror!!!!

Last year I went with the handlebars.  The year before I went with a crazy sideburn stache.  This year I am keeping it thin and dirty.  French style with a touch of Mexican.  100% greasy.  Here is how it looks so far.  Remember it is still early.
I'm in.  Started clean shaven on the first.  It will be a glorious month!
I don't know Chris.... haven't shaved off the beard in 20 years Do I still qualify That's a mean French / Mexican look you got going there    Jacques
